<HEADLINE>
<P>
BRADLEY'S TRAVELS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
With the ever increasing problems that plague Los Angeles, such as the 
homeless, gangs, the drug traffic that runs rampant on our streets and schools, 
the insufficient police allocations, the insufferable housing conditions for 
the poor, the jammed freeways and the pathetic treatment of the aged, it is 
superfluous to even attempt to justify Tom Bradley's excessive travel under the 
pretense of stimulating foreign trade and enticement of foreign travel to Los 
Angeles. 
</P>
<P>
PENNY LINK, Redlands 
</P>
</TEXT>
<GRAPHIC>
<P>
Photo, Mayor Tom Bradley in London during September trip to promote tourism. 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
