<P>
October 8, 1990, Monday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<P>
STEPHEN TUKEL; JOSHUA HORWITZ 
</P>
<SECTION>
<P>
View; Part E; Page 1; Column 5; View Desk 
