<P>
HOSTAGES CHECKED FOR RELEASE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Times Wire Services 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
BAALBECK, Lebanon 
</P>
